result:
<v-dialog
        :value="visible"
        width="500"
        persistent
>
    <v-card>
        <v-card-title
                class="headline grey lighten-2"
                primary-title
        >
            Invite user to conversation
            <v-spacer></v-spacer>
            <v-btn icon flat @click="cancel">
                <v-icon>close</v-icon>
            </v-btn>
        </v-card-title>

        <v-card-text>
            <v-text-field label="User id" v-model="userId"></v-text-field>
        </v-card-text>
        <v-card-text>
            <v-textarea :rows="2" label="Invitation message" v-model="invitationMessage"></v-textarea>
        </v-card-text>

        <v-divider></v-divider>

        <v-card-actions>
            <v-spacer></v-spacer>
            <v-btn
                    color="primary"
                    flat
                    @click="invite"
            >
                Invite
            </v-btn>
        </v-card-actions>
    </v-card>
</v-dialog>
